### 16-memory-demo · alice 第一轮：告诉助手名字
POST http://localhost:18016/memory/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "conversationId": "alice",
  "message": "我叫Alice，请记住"
}

### alice 第二轮：追问名字，应记得
POST http://localhost:18016/memory/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "conversationId": "alice",
  "message": "我叫什么名字？"
}

### bob 用不同 conversationId 追问同样问题，应不知道（会话隔离）
POST http://localhost:18016/memory/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "conversationId": "bob",
  "message": "我叫什么名字？"
}

### 查看 alice 会话当前保留的历史消息
GET http://localhost:18016/memory/history/alice

### 清空 alice 会话记忆
DELETE http://localhost:18016/memory/history/alice
